  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pure Rust audio decoding with no unsafe code",
    "Support for 15+ audio codecs including AAC, FLAC, MP3, Vorbis, ALAC",
    "Demuxing for MP4, MKV, OGG, WAV, AIFF, and CAF containers",
    "ID3v1/v2 and Vorbis Comment metadata reading",
    "Gapless playback support",
    "Automatic format and codec detection",
    "Modular architecture with feature flags",
    "High-performance with optional SIMD optimizations"
